# Optional server-side defaults. Users can also enter keys in the app UI (Settings).
# Keys entered in the UI are stored only in the browser and never committed.

# --- OpenAI (https://platform.openai.com/api-keys) ---
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o

# --- GitHub Models (FREE: https://github.com/marketplace/models) ---
# Create a fine-grained PAT with "models" read access, then:
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...
# GITHUB_MODEL=gpt-4o
